        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Anni ab incarnatjone domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi millesimo sexagesimo quarto, pontificatus vero domni
                        nostri Alexander sumi pontifitjs et universalis pape inn apostolica
                        sacratissima beati Petri apostoli Domini sede ano tertjo, rengnante domnus
                        Enricus res in Italia anno quinto, die detjmo intrante mense agusto,
                        indic(ione) secunda, in <rs key="#Villas">villa</rs> qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Confinia #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Villas #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Canals #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/2441"><placeName
                                key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Confinia #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Villas #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Canals #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ref="#places/4181">Martjana</placeName></geogName>. Petistis ad me
                        quidem in Dei nomine <persName key="#Priors" ref="#people/1599"
                            >Ieronimus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">prior</rs> pro vice domnus <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/1596">Mainardus</persName> gratja Dei <rs key="#Abbots"
                            >abas</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries">monesterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie qui
                            vocatur in <placeName ref="#places/4179">Ponposia</placeName></orgName>,
                        una per consensum et auturitatem cuncta regula monagorum deservientjum
                        eiusdem cenobio conceditore adque largitore, uti tibi in Christi nomine
                                <persName><name ref="Blancus">Blancolo</name></persName> filio
                        condam bone memorie <persName><name ref="Felix">Filiso</name></persName> cum
                        contratribus et consortibus tuis petitoris tuisque filiis et heredibus iuris
                            <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libelario nomine</rs> concedo
                        et largior seo confirmo tibi suprascripto de rem iuris proprietatis
                        monesterio Sancte Marie qui vocatur in Ponposia, idest <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortes et portjones</rs> in integrum que
                        suprascripto petitore anteam ahbuisti et detenuisti per anteriore libell(o),
                        petitores abuit et tenuit per <rs key="#Venditio">cartula
                        conparatjonis</rs>, qui est posita ipsa res in <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        qui vocatur Villa Martjana et in fundo qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/3929"><placeName
                                key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Caltjnaria</placeName></geogName> et in fundo qui vocatur <geogName
                                    key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/3930"><placeName
                                key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Masirada</placeName></geogName> seu in fundo qui vocatur <geogName
                                    key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/3931"><placeName
                                key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Ronconi</placeName></geogName> et in fundo qui vocatur <geogName
                                    key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/3932"><placeName
                                key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Castelo</placeName></geogName> adque in fundo quivocatur <geogName
                                    key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/3933"><placeName
                                key="#Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Fadignana</placeName></geogName> seu in fundo qui vocatur <geogName
                                    key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/3934"><placeName
                                key="#Fluvial_transport #Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Sullano</placeName></geogName>, qui est posita ipsa res per
                        singulis lotjs altum vel planum, teris et <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>,
                        salectis, satjonabilibus, harbustis, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >arboribus</rs>, pomiferis et infructiferis, cultis vel incultis, <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">valibus</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscatjonibus</rs>, <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >venatjonibus</rs>, <rs key="#Houses">case</rs> seo et <rs
                            key="#Casalia">casalibus</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">occupatjonibus</rs> suis
                        et cum omnibus sibi pertinentibus, sit infra <rs key="#Plebs">blebem</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Land_clearing #Venditio #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Villas #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Hay/fodder #Eggs #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Plebs"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1486">Sancti Stefani qui vocatur in Villa
                            Martjana</orgName>, <rs key="#Confinia">inter fines</rs> ipsius fundi: a
                        primo llatere corigio <placeName key="#Confinia">Avisiani</placeName>
                        desendentem in <rs key="#Pagus">pagino</rs> de <placeName key="#Pagus"
                            >Breuse</placeName> desendentem in <placeName>Coriago</placeName>,
                        secundo llatere <rs key="#Canals">fosa</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Confinia #Canals">It(a)la</placeName> desendentem in <rs
                            key="#Canals">fosado</rs> de <placeName key="#Confinia #Canals"
                            >Cornaria</placeName>, tertjo llatere <rs key="#Canals">rupta</rs> de
                            <placeName key="#Confinia #Canals">Ficole</placeName> desendentem ad
                            <placeName key="#Rivers #Confinia" ref="#places/4646">Adicem</placeName>
                        adque a quarto llatere Adicem percorentem. Hec omnia quod superius legitur
                        concedo tibi abendum, tenendum, posidendum, laborandum, <rs
                            key="#Land_clearing">roncandum</rs>, propaginandum, supersedendum,
                        defensandum seo meliorandum in annis advenientibus viginti et novem ad
                        renovandum, ad salva caltjaria domnica dandum libell(um) renovetur. Ita sane
                        ut inferatis domice ratjonibus mihi suprascripto patrone meis supcesoribus
                        tibi suprascripto petitore meisque filiis et heredibus de labore quem
                        Dominus supra ipsum locum condonare dignatus est <rs key="#Levies"
                            >terratico</rs> de <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">grano</rs> in campo capa
                        quarta, traendas ad area et tritulatum per te petitore, <rs key="#Legumes"
                            >faba</rs> inn area modio quarto, <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >sicale</rs> in campo capa quinta, <rs key="#Cereals">mesturia
                            ingranata</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">fare</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Maiores">ordeo</rs> in campo capa quinta, traendas ad
                        area et tritulatum per te petitore, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores"
                        >trisico</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">mileo</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores">panico</rs> inn area modio sessto, <rs
                            key="#Linen">lino</rs> mana detjma gramulata, <rs key="#Legumes"
                            >tjsercia</rs> seu <rs key="#Legumes">lenticula</rs> inn area stario
                        quinto, de <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> modio quarto, duabus vitjbus arbore
                        pecto ponentem a pedes tritulatum et postea petitore cesum; et si vinea
                        pastenaveritis, post in torta pervenerit, fruere debeatis amnis septem et
                        postea redere debeatis modio quarto; et roncon sit roncaveritis, fruere
                        debeatis amnis quinque et postea redere debeatis sicut de ceterra tera et
                            <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">vale</rs>, si di sui
                            <rs>graveritis</rs> fruere debeatis amnis tres et postea redere debeatis
                        sicut superius legitur. Concedo tibi suprascripto petitore casale uno
                        extendentem in lonco <rs key="#Size">perticas detjmpedas viginti et in lato
                            similiter</rs>; <rs key="#Exenia">exenio</rs> vero pro ipso casale <rs
                            key="#Poultry">pullo</rs> uno et <rs key="#Eggs">ovas</rs> quinque, de
                        grano manumlitere stario uno; et si <rs key="#Pigs">portj</rs> abueritis pro
                            <rs key="#Acorns #Levies">clandatico</rs> dare debeatis de decem portj
                        porco uno; pervectum sicut ipsum terraticum aridum vel liquidum per te
                        petitore vel per meum misum usque ad ripa ubi <rs key="#Fluvial_transport"
                            >nave vestra domnica</rs> potuit pervenire. Maiore quidem domnico vel
                        mea dominatjone cum onore et bodientja susipere debeatis et supseptjoneis
                        facere sine aliquo dolo vel fraude. Et non abeatis licentja de ipsa res nec
                        vindere nec donare vel comutuare nisi inter vos petitores. Et non abeatis
                        licentja de ipsa suprascripta res ad nulum platjtum plubicum neque districta
                        andare nisi ad me suprascripto ordinatore et meis supcesoribus tibi
                        suprascripto petitore tuisque filiis et heredibus ipsa res quod superius
                        legitur stare et defensare et auturiare promipto usque a perfinitus tempus
                        quod superius legitur. Si quis vero parte [c]ontra os libellum ire
                        temtaverit non observaveriti usque ad finitum tempus, de pars parti fidem
                        servanti ante omnes litis initjum vel interpelatjone, pene nomine, <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi untjas quartuor</rs> et post penam solutam
                        manentem hos libelum sicut superius legitur in suo robore et firmitatem.
                        Quam vero ec paginam <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Martinus"
                                >Martinus</name></persName> Christi misericordia <rs key="#Tabellio"
                            >tabelio</rs> de vico qui vocatur Villa Martjana scribendum rogavit et
                        supter manus mea propria firmavi ad abendum et detinendum sicut superius
                        legitur, sup die, mense et indic(ione) secunda, in villa qui vocatur
                        Martjana. (C) Ego Mainard(us) abb(as) huic lib(e)ll(um) m(anu) m(ea)
                        s(ub)s(cripsi). + Pet(r)us monahus in hoc libello s(ub)s(cripsi).</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
